rhost (1.2) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Can use .rhost.d directory for YAML templates.
  * Added -V|--variables-file option to read variable settings from a file.
  * Properly process quotes in linux/windows terminal commands.
  * Insert hostname, domainname, and fqdn into template variables.

